column13: A program/piece of software that imitates human behaviour in order to carry out conversations with humans over the internet or via an interface.
An ai that attempts to replicate human conversation
A chatbot is a computer program with human capabilities. They are designed to interact intelligently with humans in different forms of communication i.e. voice, text
Artificial Intelligence capable of holding a conversation through the use of automated responses
